            . On the 30th of June I saw the pri<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="182609140134"></xptr>soner take four brooms from Mrs. Ife's shop, and walk away - he had not gone above a hundred yards, when I told a person, who went and took him; I was at a window on a ladder; I had a full view of him.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18260914-318-person1710">
                  THOMAS 
                  SYMONS
